Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:02.58,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:419127,422589}I was chosen for the national team,\Nand yet I gave in and fled the training camp.{NOTE:せっかく選手に選ばれながら特訓に負けて逃げ出して…}
