Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.86,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:449824,450867}No…!{NOTE:いや！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.07,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:450867,452077}I've had enough!{NOTE:いやなのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.32,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:452077,453328}{NOTE:いや！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.41,Alternative,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:453328,454412}{NOTE:もう…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.83,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:455872,457832}To hell with volleyball!{NOTE:もうバレーなんか嫌だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.38,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:459918,463380}I escaped from you.{NOTE:私あなた達から逃げ出した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:48.46,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:463380,468468}But I still didn't forget how miserable I felt back then.{NOTE:でも、でもあの時の惨めな思いは今でも忘れてなんかいないわ、私。}
