Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.60,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:478228,482607}On the contrary, I didn't want to stay labeled as a loser for the rest of my life.{NOTE:それより私だって一生負けるでなんかいたくないってそう思って…}
