Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.52,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:563605,565523}– Long time no see!\N– Finally.{NOTE:—わっ、しばらく！\\N—しばらく！\\N—わっ、よかったわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:29.19,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:565523,569194}– How have you been?\N– You got all pretty.{NOTE:—元気そうね。皆ね。\\N—皆綺麗に成っちゃって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:34.36,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:569194,574365}Seeing us like that, I remember of America, the camp at Miyazaki and Coach Inokuma.{NOTE:皆揃うと宮崎アメリカそれに猪野熊コーチXX思い出すXXよ。}
