Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.76,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:600391,602769}Actually, Coach is my older brother.{NOTE:あのコーチが私の兄だったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.06,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:603770,605063}Huh…?{NOTE:え～？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:605063,606146}Huh!?{NOTE:あ～？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.77,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:607440,608775}Kozue, you knew?{NOTE:こずえ、知ってた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:608775,609859}Hm? Yes.{NOTE:え？ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:13.48,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:609859,613488}Wow, that's cold. Why didn't you tell me?{NOTE:わ～、水臭い。教えてくれないなんてさ。}
