Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.40,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:615323,616407}Let's see…{NOTE:えっと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.45,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:616407,619452}"Michiru, you're still playing volleyball\Nlike we promised, are you?"{NOTE:「美智留。約束通りバレーを続けているようだね。」}
