Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:28.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:625917,628211}"But this time, they'll be your opponents."{NOTE:「今度は敵にかたとして。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:629003,632090}"Remember, your opponents aren't your enemies."{NOTE:「しかし敵と破綻に戦う相手ではない。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:37.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:632090,637387}"The stronger your opponent is, the stronger you have to be."{NOTE:「強い敵に対して負けまいとする意思がおのずからを強くして行く。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:637387,639681}"When you play against strong opponents…"{NOTE:「そういう相手を好適してというが…」}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:44.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:639681,644769}"…you can give your best shot and have a memorable sporting event."{NOTE:「…君たちがそれぞれ好敵手となって立派な試合をしてくれることを。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:47.18,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:644769,647188}"Best regards, from the far side of the ocean."{NOTE:「遥か海の彼方から祈っている。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.23,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:647939,650233}Yeah… It's like he says.{NOTE:んん。その通りだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.86,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:650233,651860}We won't lose.{NOTE:内は絶対に負けないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.19,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:651860,653194}Neither will we.{NOTE:私だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.78,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:653194,656781}Well, if I were you, I'd wait to talk.{NOTE:まっ、あなたたちXX不足なし。}
