Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:47.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063896,1067024}Unbelievable. They're even stronger than before.{NOTE:鮮やか。前より破壊力もうついてるようだし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073990,1075533}That block…{NOTE:あの壁。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075533,1078286}We have to overcome that block.{NOTE:あの壁が乗り越えられなければ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.03,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078286,1081038}I see Jidōin players aren't called queens for nothing.{NOTE:さすが寺堂院は王者風格ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.33,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081038,1082331}Yes, just like we expected.{NOTE:はい。予想通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090256,1093092}Before we can play with Jidōin, we must face Aoba Academy.{NOTE:寺堂院の前の敵。青葉学園。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.13,Alternative,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094927,1097138}Please watch how far that coward went.{NOTE:負け犬の強さを見てちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:25.52,Alternative,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101726,1105521}She's not from college.\NShe's our captain, Yamamoto Misao-san.{NOTE:大学生じゃないわよ。キャプテンの山本みさおさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:29.44,Alternative,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105521,1109442}Don't tell me you're afraid of them just because they're a popular sports school.{NOTE:まさかスポーツの盛んな学校だからと恐れてるわけじゃ…？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:33.65,Alternative,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109442,1113654}Ayuhara-san, make sure you don't lose\Nuntil we play together.{NOTE:鮎原さん。内達と戦うまで負けるのはいかないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:38.90,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113654,1118909}The bond with your rivals is what makes both of you develop further.{NOTE:敵とはお互いに励ましあって、お互いを成長させていく好敵。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.70,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118909,1120703}Develop further…{NOTE:好敵。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.07,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120703,1122079}I don't want to lose.{NOTE:私は負けたくない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:48.08,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1122079,1128085}{\fad(500,750)}Rest in peace, Ichinose Tsutomu{NOTE:故一ノ瀬努の墓}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:48.08,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123205,1128085}I want Kozue-kun to become the world's best attacker.{NOTE:僕はこずえくんに望む。世界のアタックナンバーワンに成ってほしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:57.84,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136844,1137845}What do you think?{NOTE:どうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137845,1141307}Jidōin High School style is really impressive. Right, Ayuhara?{NOTE:寺堂院高校の戦いぶりは堂々としてるな。鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141307,1142642}Hm? Ah, yes.{NOTE:あっ？はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:09.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142642,1149065}All teams of this tournament have probably set themselves the goal of beating Jidōin.{NOTE:おそらく今大会の全チームが妥当寺堂院を目指しているのを知っているはずなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:12.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149065,1152526}They're not conscious of it at all.{NOTE:彼女らはまったくそれを意識していない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:16.19,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152526,1156197}They're just focused on the match, full of confidence.{NOTE:ただ自身を持って、確実に戦っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:19.99,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156197,1159992}It's an attitude truly worth of a champion.{NOTE:あれが王者の風格というものだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159992,1161118}Wouldn't you agree?{NOTE:そうじゃないかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.84,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1178511,1180846}Ayuhara{NOTE:鮎原}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.77,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186227,1187770}Time's up.{NOTE:さあ、時間よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.35,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187770,1189355}It's our turn.{NOTE:いよいよ戦い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189355,1192817}Captain, I can't get out of my head what Coach Hongou said before…{NOTE:あの、キャプテン。さっき本郷コーチが仰っていたこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:53.81,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192817,1193818}Ah.{NOTE:あっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.02,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193818,1195027}What did he say?{NOTE:あのこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195027,1197530}I'd like to ask all of you for a favor.{NOTE:ええ。皆にもお願いしたいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197530,1200032}Please don't think about Aoba Academy.{NOTE:青葉学園に意識しないで欲しいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200032,1202868}Forget that they're a sports school.{NOTE:相手がスポーツ高だってことも忘れてしまって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202868,1206789}I just want you to focus on the match\Nand give your best.{NOTE:ただ全力を出し切って、戦いことだけを考えて欲しいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206789,1210334}It's what Jidōin High School does.\NNothing more, nothing less.{NOTE:寺堂院高校だって結局それだけで戦ってるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210334,1212586}If we focus on what's right, we can win.{NOTE:全力を出しきれる時勝てる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212586,1215214}I want you to remember that simple thing.{NOTE:その簡単な事を思い出して欲しいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:18.59,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215214,1218592}I want you to become the world's best attacker.{NOTE:君が世界のアタックナンバーワンに成ってくれること狙っているよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:25.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221971,1225182}It all boils down to whether we can fight at our full power.{NOTE:全力をつくせるかつくせないか、それだけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228352,1229937}That's all there is to it.{NOTE:それだけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229937,1231605}I'm counting on you, girls.{NOTE:皆、頼むわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:32.64,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1232106,1232648}Right.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.69,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1232648,1233691}Let's do our best.{NOTE:頑張ろうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.52,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1233691,1234524}Yeah.{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:46.37,Default,Yagisawa Kaori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244869,1246370}Here they come.{NOTE:コートより簡単なことね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.91,Default,Yagisawa Kaori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246370,1249915}Ah, Ayuhara-san, it's been long time.{NOTE:あ、鮎原さん、いよいよね。お久しぶり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249915,1252710}Congratulations on your victory.{NOTE:寺堂院高校快勝だったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:56.00,Default,Yagisawa Shizuka,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252710,1256005}Have you gotten better at three player volleyball?{NOTE:三人バレーの試合意外調子はどうだいやろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256005,1258424}Thanks to you, we got a little better.{NOTE:おかげさまで上々よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:02.34,Default,Yagisawa Kaori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258424,1262344}Promise us we'll meet in the finals.{NOTE:約束だね。今度の決勝戦でコンマの決戦するゆうたん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262344,1263679}All right.{NOTE:分かってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:04.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263679,1264930}You may rely on it.{NOTE:必ず。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.93,Default,Yagisawa Katsura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264930,1267933}I can't wait to see how good you got.{NOTE:XのぐらいXXX楽しみやな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.93,Default,Yagisawa Kaori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267933,1270936}I'll watch your whole game from beginning to end.{NOTE:あんたらの試合ゆっくりと見せてもらうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270936,1272313}See you later.{NOTE:じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:16.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272897,1276776}Jidōin High School won't cherish their champion title for much longer.{NOTE:寺堂院高校にいつまでも王者の地位を預けてはいけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:37.79,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296879,1297797}Professor…{NOTE:先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.68,Blackboard,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1306138,1308682}Fujimi · Aoba{NOTE:富士見・青葉学園}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.06,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309099,1312061}What are you doing, Ayuhara-san? That's not good!{NOTE:これはいけない。鮎原さんXXちょっとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:57.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316482,1317316}Midori!{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317316,1318192}Double attack, right?{NOTE:ダブルアタックね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:11.87,Blackboard,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1330579,1331872}Fujimi · Aoba{NOTE:富士見・青葉学園}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:15.50,Default,Yagisawa Katsura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332081,1335501}What is this? They lead Fujimi by the nose.\NIt should've been the other way around.{NOTE:何よ、富士見高校XXXもってるわ。あんなXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.75,Default,Yagisawa Katsura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335501,1336752}For crying out loud.{NOTE:ほんまに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:19.58,Default,Yagisawa Shizuka,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336752,1339588}They let them score another point…{NOTE:又点取られてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.84,Default,Yagisawa Kaori,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339588,1341841}Let's hold with judgment until after the game.{NOTE:試合は終わりまでにXX分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:40.23,Blackboard,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1352685,1360234}Fujimi · Aoba{NOTE:富士見・青葉学園}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.99,Blackboard,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1367074,1368993}Fujimi · Aoba{NOTE:富士見・青葉学園}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:51.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369827,1371996}We can't lose like this.{NOTE:このまま負けるなんて絶対にできない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:53.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371996,1373998}Tsutomu-kun, protect me!{NOTE:努くん。私を守って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:57.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375958,1377167}Ah!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:03.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382673,1383756}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:13.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389597,1393934}Tsutomu-kun is the reason why I'm still on the court here today.{NOTE:私は一度捨てたコートに努くんを励まして戻ってきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:17.10,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393934,1397104}I'm sure he watches over me.{NOTE:努くんは私を見ていてくれる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.10,0:23:18.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397104,1398689}I'll show him a splendid double attack!{NOTE:そのためのダブルアタック。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:25.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1402484,1405154}I'll show him the vanishing spike!{NOTE:そのための消えるスパイク。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405154,1406780}Midori! Double attack!{NOTE:みどり！ダブルアタック！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:29.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408157,1409617}Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:31.57,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1410284,1411577}Here it is!{NOTE:来た！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:32.57,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411577,1412578}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:34.66,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412578,1414663}Help… help me out!{NOTE:私を…私を守って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414663,1416790}You left me behind.{NOTE:私は戦いに生き残りたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:39.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416790,1419251}I need to live while you're gone!{NOTE:努くんの分も生き残りたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1419251,1420793}Lend me your strength!{NOTE:守って！}
