Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:06.61,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1440064,1446612}During the game against Aoba Academy, Kozue sees late Tsutomu's figure in the stands.{NOTE:青葉との試合中死んだはずの努の姿をスタンドの中に見たこずえの心には迷いがあった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:10.11,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1446612,1450115}But the merciless attack of Yamamoto and Shirakawa continues on.{NOTE:しかし山本と白河の容赦ない攻撃の舞。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:13.24,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1450115,1453243}Fujimi finds itself in a tight spot.{NOTE:富士見絶対絶命のピンチを迎えた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.66,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1453243,1455663}"Tsutomu-kun watches over us."{NOTE:努くんが見守っていてくれるこの試合。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.58,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1455663,1457581}"I have to win no matter what."{NOTE:なんとしても勝たなければ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:22.33,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1457581,1462336}As Kozue is about to spike, a vision of Tsutomu emerges before her eyes.{NOTE:祈るようにして打つこずえのスパイクの前に努の幻が浮かび上がる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:25.58,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1462336,1465589}Please next forward to the next episode.{NOTE:次回「アタックナンバーワン」にご期待ください。}
